data.description: This charming townhouse in Dawsonville, Georgia offers a cozy and modern living space. With three bedrooms and two and a half baths, this home provides ample room for everyone to have their own personal space. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a lovely white modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, including a gas stove. The bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, providing a peaceful retreat away from the hustle and bustle of the main living areas. Home has new interior paint and will be like new after new carpet installed! One notable feature of this home is the storage closet located at the back of the house, which is equipped with power for added convenience. Other updates include the recently replaced HVAC system in 2021 and a four-year-old water heater. Additionally, the gutters have been recently cleaned. This townhouse is perfectly situated just two minutes away from downtown Dawsonville, allowing you to easily access all the local amenities, shops, and restaurants. Additionally, the north Georgia Premium Outlets are just a short 12-minute drive away, making it a shopper's paradise.
